text: A federal appeals court revived a legal challenge Friday to California prison security rules that allow some female inmates — but no males — to buy or possess a wide range of items including tweezers, bath towels, jeans and sugary foods like honey or jam. https://t.co/p8d7MYldRA

text: Warriors president Rick Welts tweeted a message of support to Raptors president Masai Ujiri after body-camera footage emerged this week of an Oracle Arena security guard aggressively shoving him after his team clinched the championship in 2019. https://t.co/3On8Z4sjQ5
